  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You have taken it upon yourself to learn the ways of combat to aid with your tasks, perhaps in a role as a corrector. You are trained with the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.e4NwsnPnpQKbDZ9F]{Composite Shortbow}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.vlnzTSsRmWeSkt9O]{Glaive}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.aXuJh4i8HqSu6NYV]{Longspear}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.LJdbVTOZog39EEbi]{Longsword}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.hIgqLgH3YcLZBeoT]{Shortbow}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.tOhoGvmCMw4JpWcS]{Spear}. You also gain access to all uncommon conrasu weapons(@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.7WRzbBTOCsJx5f7L]{Buugeng}). For the purpose of determining your proficiency, martial conrasu weapons are simple weapons and advanced conrasu weapons are martial weapons.</p>"
